Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.38,0:01:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是重要的人柱候補
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果身體垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓我頭痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.41,0:01:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬可醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底想讓我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你們在做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用這個國家和所有的國民製造巨大的鍊成陣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了製作賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說對了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.69,0:02:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過方向對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方向？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不協助的話就把那個村子消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從拉斯多那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們不對那個村子出手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助我們毀滅所有國民？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不協助我們讓那個村子的人被消滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄小就能拯救大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想想就能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這才是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起理論 感情為先
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前我殺死的男人也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成那傢伙的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就沒法出手 讓逆轉的機會逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太容易鑽空子真是太方便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.08,0:03:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類居然讓你這麼費勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓斯卡逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連庫拉多尼也被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.43,0:03:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否認
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有點開心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活了六十年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在站在國家的頂點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都如父親大人預計的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有外國來的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連老謀深算的我們也被耍得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定年輕人的時代已經不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普萊德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯 你和人類接觸的時間太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘了我們是怎樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那些叛逆的發言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不向父親大人報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從憲兵隊的情報來分析 已經知道大致的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停住 中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別刺激他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目標是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳 要離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肚子裡還養了怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把周圍的東西都吞進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然造出了這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 好不容易抓住的人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的生命優先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他記住了我們的臉和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有放他活著回去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把火焰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你給我辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 別跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的目標可是大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃進那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.07,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 居然在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德他們還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能死在這種亂七八糟的戰鬥裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊·馬斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誘餌騙到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來相當生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點回去 你這沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉坐這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我灰溜溜地逃回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下會礙手礙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的派不上用場 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個呆子大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去幹你該幹的活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的領袖是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是能放著不管的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是布拉德雷大總統？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個話題等會再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經滿員了吧 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.59,0:08:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能把小孩子留在戰場上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的戰鬥對手是軍隊高層吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得從庫拉多尼口中探出情報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們留在這裡和他戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和是不是小孩子沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次提出作戰的是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫助我們到這份上 真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:08:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道用法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺人的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是保護你們生命的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的手不是殺人的手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我借走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭芳就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣是會早死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅伊·馬斯坦古在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把拉斯多…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也太恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格也全變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣才能抓住它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下 庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.74,0:10:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是水蚤草履蟲小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來回收庫拉多尼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想和小不點打架…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五研究所的地下說了五次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說你忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那針對某件事情的記憶力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人費神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現馬斯坦古了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯多的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞 吞 把他吞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克兄弟也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.76,0:11:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也感覺到氣息了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有幾個人？人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉斯對砍的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是清國皇帝第十二子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.04,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吞他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不能對我們兄弟出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟 那邊拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和拉斯不相上下的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 傑利姆的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被評為班上第一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你寫進作文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我能讀讀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話就太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親是亞美斯多利斯國的大總統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個國家拚命幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親心中所想的一直是這個國家的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家能和平地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在解決很多問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不論多忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親也不會忘記家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.83,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他愛著我 愛著母親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我的話 父親一直都會側耳傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我的願望 父親一直會認真地聽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡我的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 傑利姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上當了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們人類沒法做到這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你是想被絞死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想被咬死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.87,0:13:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說被砍死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 那麼就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用攻擊眼睛這種下三濫的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從小時候就一直在防範暗殺的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯規的技術也不得不學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能乖乖被抓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要長生不老的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想被折磨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區人類別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別小看人類 人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.18,0:14:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能吃你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃剛才的細線眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 別妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 不能讓他把人柱吞進去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 麟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 吐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把哥哥吐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 已經吞下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的 這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有老婆和孩子用過的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開燈太多會讓鄰居懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我的床上忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去少主身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這身體能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 那麼直接去司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這機會區分一下己方和敵方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都這副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的傷還沒好呢 還想再亂來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統也許是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間慢慢等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把孩子們留在戰場上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不行動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為大人怎麼樹立榜樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 被大佐當成小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果愛德華君聽到了也許會生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是照搬了妳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 讓我很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐居然會走這大膽的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是從周邊開始入手而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠理解你和支持你的人 能多一個就多一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點遲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算聽從他的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.91,0:18:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是光榮之門還是魔窟的入口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉在這裡等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.49,0:18:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一個人逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能受命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定會回來的 妳等著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 祝您好運
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是羅伊·馬斯坦古嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才妻子給我打電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文中將閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到任以來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太過繁忙沒能到訪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日又是深夜造訪非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說古拉曼那狡猾老頭還精神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就11連敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是12
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次你還是下得不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是意識到勝利之後下得太爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.47,0:19:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說我太天真了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不能完全捨棄感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雷文一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央的雷文將軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很優秀 但是對感情很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經親自去救負傷的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打亂了陣容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子有多少棋子都不夠用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居 居然如此侮辱我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是因為拯救部下的決心而被中央賞識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才到中央任職
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒有被邊境的老頭說三道四的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一提
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這句話惹您生氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明將軍還是正義之士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都可以和您商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉曼中將這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被那狐狸擺了一道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到會議的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去會議室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經習慣中央都市了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 雖然想和市民多多交流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市井的傳聞也不能忽視
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多數是無足輕重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡給貓餵食什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死的人出現了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統是人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 沒有搞笑細胞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是古拉曼的部下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面沒有學到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是那種小傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能成為大家茶餘飯後的話題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人進這種…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 剛才的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統是人造人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 馬斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是人造人所以怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 休斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊裡不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說軍隊有危機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是指軍隊本身有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裡是地獄深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.03,0:22:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 這是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找消失的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由於懼怕孤獨嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使不見身影也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.22,0:24:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第25話 黑暗之門
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:06.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}純白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:12.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即將起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:24.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不斷變化的地圖裡 攙雜著各種夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:36.97,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我這微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:43.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那雲的彼端嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:44.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.69,0:00:46.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}卻受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:49.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}彷彿看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}從天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}點點雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反復的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}筆直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:05.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}並不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的殘影烙印在兩眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在這片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:27.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾見過的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:33.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:37.36,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:44.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人這樣描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:49.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上塗鴉的花也會搖動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:55.54,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:57.82,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫長的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:01.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去與獲取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:08.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:16.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚也好  痛苦也好  都將化為恆星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:22.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點燃照亮明天的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:27.55,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起小手  兩個人一起創造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:32.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜尋星塵與光芒四射的永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:38.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 那天也許還會降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:44.07,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季節依然在不斷地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:48.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有點迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:52.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:56.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}請讓我維持到永遠


